Describe the most notable examples of leadership you have observed over the past year.
Over the past year, I had the opportunity to witness several instances of inspiring leadership. One notable example was when a team leader took charge during a critical project crisis by implementing innovative solutions and effectively coordinating efforts among team members. This resulted in a successful completion of the project despite initial setbacks. Another instance involved a manager who consistently demonstrated empathy and understanding towards employees, fostering a positive work environment that improved employee morale and productivity.
